@page "/about"
@inject HttpClient Http

    <div class="container">
        <div class="row row-no-gutters">
            <div class="col-sm-10 ">
                <div class="card shadow-sm border-0">
                    <div class="card-header text-center border-0">
                        <h4 class="">Test By Direct Input</h4>
                    </div>
                    <div class="card-body">
                        <p>
                            Readability is the ease with which a reader can understand a written text. Readability scores are an approximation calculated using different readability formula. This Readability Testing tool can find readability score, age group and grade to understand the given writing using a different formula. This tool can also find the number of characters, words, sentences in given writing.
                        </p>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="card shadow-sm border-0 mt-4">
                    <div class="card-header text-center border-0 font-weight-bold">
                        Readability formula
                    </div>
                    <div class="card-body">
                        <h5>Flesch-Kincaid Grade Level</h5>
                        Originally created to analyze the readabiliity of technical material. Now used widely and highly regarded for its reliability. Suitable for the grading of a wide range of writing and for all ages.<a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Flesch%E2%80%93Kincaid_readability_tests" target="_blank">Learn More.</a>

                    </div>
                    <div class="card-body">
                        <h5>Coleman-Liau Index</h5>
                        A character-calculated formula suitable for a wide range of texts and for all ages, and especially useful within education.<a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Flesch%E2%80%93Kincaid_readability_tests" target="_blank">Learn More.</a>
                    </div>
                    <div class="card-body">
                        <h5>SMOG Index</h5>
                        Applicable to a range of texts and ages but has been proven particularly useful in healthcare literature.<a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/SMOG" target="_blank">Learn More.</a>
                    </div>
                    <div class="card-body">
                        <h5>Automated Readability Index</h5>
                        A character-calculated formula suitable for a wide range of texts and ages but proven especially useful in technical writing.<a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Automated_readability_index" target="_blank">Learn More.</a>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>